    "time-content": {
        "title": "Words based on time",
        "content": [
            {
                "title": "Now lets learn some words based on time.",
                "details": "1. Usually nouns revolving around time will have the time particle appended (에) when you reference them in a sentence.<br/>2. To make a sentence with time, the number of the hour uses native Korean numbers, and the minute number uses Sino-Korean numbers. Thus, to say 3:29pm, it would be 오후 (afternoon) + 세시(3 hours) + 이십구분(29 minutes)."
            }
        ],
